         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">8/10/82 ¶  ¶ Your no. 919, dear Mr Tepper, is the rare ( ¶ Acrotriche ¶ )  ¶ Styphelia depressa ¶ . I do not remember having had the fruit before.  ¶ 918 Pterostylis nana R.Br. (new locality). ¶  ¶ Do...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">82.10.08a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotated by Tepper: 'Reply 2.11.82'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>8/10/82</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihre N. 919, lieber Herr Tepper, ist die seltne (Acrotriche) <name key="Styphelia%20depressa">Styphelia depressa</name>. Ich erinnere nicht, die Frucht vorher gehabt zu haben.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">918 <name key="Pterostylis%20nana">Pterostylis nana</name> RBr (neuer Standort).</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Seien Sie nicht ungeduldig, wenn Sie nicht von allen Probebögen des Arten-Census einen Abdruck erhalten, ich habe nur etwa ½ Dutz zum Vertheilen. Übrigens wird ja der vollendete Band Ende dieses Jahres erscheinen und Ihnen dann zu kommen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit besten Wünschen für Ihr Wohlergehen</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Bei <name key="Agaricus%20">Agaricus </name>Pilzen und anderen Hymenomyceten ist es erforderlich, die Farbe, wie solche frisch erscheint, anzugeben. In dieser Weise waren Ihre letzten Notizen sehr gut.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">8/10/82</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your no. 919, dear Mr Tepper, is the rare (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">Acrotriche</seg>) <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Styphelia%20depressa">Styphelia depressa</name>
               </seg>. I do not remember having had the fruit before. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">918 <name key="Pterostylis%20nana">Pterostylis nana</name> R.Br. (new locality).</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Do not be impatient if you do not receive a print of all galley proofs of the species census,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">B83.03.04.</p>
               </note> I have only about ½ dozen for distribution. After all, the completed volume will certainly appear at the end of this year and then come to you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With best wishes for your welfare</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">In the case of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Agaricus</seg> fungi and other Hymenomycetes it is necessary to indicate the colour as it appears fresh. In this way your last notes were very good.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Acrotriche%20depressa">Acrotriche depressa</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Agaricus%20">Agaricus </name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Pterostylis%20nana">Pterostylis nana</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Styphelia%20depressa">Styphelia depressa</name>
            </p>
         </div>
